      &lt;img alt="A marketing image of the Google TV Streamer." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/znrOeDFXcIAEdRVrsRHIU-3Pq1Q=/0x29:2040x1389/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73504380/streamer.0.jpg" /&gt;
